 beautiful paradise is one of the most dangerous waves in the world known as Teahupo\\u00ca\\u00bbo.\", \"from\": 284, \"to\": 390, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a beautiful paradise\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"the most dangerous waves\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 369}, {\"ngram\": \"Teahupo\\u00ca\\u00bbo\", \"from\": 379, \"to\": 389}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This massive wave will serve as the arena for the best surfers to represent their countries and possibly live out their dreams of winning an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This massive wave\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 408}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"the best surfers\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"their countries\", \"from\": 467, \"to\": 482}, {\"ngram\": \"their dreams\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 529, \"to\": 545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One surfer who is primed to do well in Tahiti isBrisa Hennessy.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999833785297, \"rank\": 1.6621169758809574e-08, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}, {\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"score\": 0.9999999968526936, \"rank\": 3.1243654510842037e-09, \"text\": \"Hennessy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One surfer\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She will represent her home nation of Costa Rica in Tahiti in July.\", \"from\": 612, \"to\": 679,