.org/resource/Shiseido\"}, {\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"score\": 0.9999999833785297, \"rank\": 1.6621169758809574e-08, \"text\": \"Tahiti\", \"types\": [\"Q23442\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tahiti\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teahupo\\u00ca\\u00bbo\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"this exact wave\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 802}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the event Hennessy sat down with Fansided to discuss an array of topics including her massive WSL Championship Tour season, the upcoming Olympic Games, and more.\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 887, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"score\": 0.9999999968526936, \"rank\": 3.1243654510842037e-09, \"text\": \"Hennessy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 878}, {\"ngram\": \"Fansided\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 910}, {\"ngram\": \"an array\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 930}, {\"ngram\": \"topics\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"her massive WSL Championship Tour season\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Olympic Games\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1019}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Teahupo\\u00ca\\u00bbo is this really unique wave, unlike any other wave on Earth, it's powerful, dangerous, beautiful,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Teahupo\\u00ca\\u00bbo\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"this really unique wave\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"any other wave\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1093}, {\"ngram\": \"Earth\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You can get the wave of your life out there.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wave\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1173}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 1177, \"to\": 1186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So you have to go into it with such an open kind of mindset with clear goals and kind of no expectations.\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such an open kind\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"mindset\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"clear goals\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1274}, {\"ngram\": \"kind of no expectations\", \"from\": 1279, \"to\": 1302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And for me to get that experience and work with some of the local heroes there, I was working with Tereva David, and he's one of the best out there, just to get his insight was life-changing for me, and I think gave me that confidence going into the Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that experience\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"the local heroes\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1376}, {\"ngram\": \"Tereva David\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1415}, {\"ngram\": \"his insight\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"that confidence\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to her physical preparation for theOlympic Games, Hennessy is working to improve her mental game as well.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1628, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"score\": 0.9999999968526936, \"rank\": 3.1243654510842037e-09, \"text\": \"Hennessy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"her physical preparation\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Games\", \"from\": 1610, \"to\": 1626}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental game\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1674}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has been utilizing a positive mindset to stay present at game time.\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1755, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a positive mindset\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1725}, {\"ngram\": \"game time\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being a part of the WSL tour can be tough mentally, with travel and competition.\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6947972701392334e-23, \"text\": \"WSL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Surf_League\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 1762, \"to\": 1768}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 1824, \"to\": 1835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hennessy spoke about staying focused on the task at hand and not willing to much into the future.\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1934, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hennessy\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1845}, {\"ngram\": \"the task\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 1889, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"the future\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1933}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think, the last year and kind of coming into this year, I have really realized how important the mental side,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this year\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"how important the mental side\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am learning how to navigate my way of, kind of balancing my life and the person I am inside and out of the water.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2176, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my way\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2142}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2166, \"to\": 2175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am kind of fulfilling both roles in that way where I need to meet my happiness goals as a human and I think that brings out my best self out in the water.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both roles\", \"from\": 2201, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"that way\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"my happiness goals\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"a human\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"my best self\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2315}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2323, \"to\": 2332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have just kind of been preparing on going in with no expectations and not thinking in this futuristic mindset.\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no expectations\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2401}, {\"ngram\": \"this futuristic mindset\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like surfing is a very present sport, and when you are out in the water, all that matters is what's in front of you, and I have been trying to practice that more.\\\"\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very present sport\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2490}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2525}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the focus on happiness at the forefront, Hennessy has another project that she has recently become involved with.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2665, \"end\": 2673, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"score\": 0.9999999968526936, \"rank\": 3.1243654510842037e-09, \"text\": \"Hennessy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the focus\", \"from\": 2624, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"happiness\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"the forefront\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"another project\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has partnered with Eventbrite and haspicked out several events in Southern Californiathat she would like to recommend to the public and her followers.\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2808, \"end\": 2816, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999676974372579, \"rank\": 3.230075882142828e-05, \"text\": \"Southern\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Southern_United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eventbrite\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"several events\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"the public\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2873}, {\"ngram\": \"her followers\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the events involve the outdoors, such as yoga and meditation.\", \"from\": 2893, \"to\": 2962, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 2901, \"to\": 2911}, {\"ngram\": \"the outdoors\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2932}, {\"ngram\": \"yoga\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2946}, {\"ngram\": \"meditation\", \"from\": 2951, \"to\": 2961}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other events are based on Hennessy's creative side like poetry writing and cooking.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2989, \"end\": 2997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"score\": 0.9999999968526936, \"rank\": 3.1243654510842037e-09, \"text\": \"Hennessy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hennessy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other events\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"poetry writing\", \"from\": 3019, \"to\": 3033}, {\"ngram\": \"cooking\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hennessy uses writing in her own life to allow herself to share her passions.\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hennessy\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3055}, {\"ngram\": \"her own life\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"her passions\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think about Eventbrite and how they are really just bringing connection and passions and things that interest you, and I feel that is something that the world needs more of,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3141, \"end\": 3151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventbrite\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Eventbrite\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventbrite\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eventbrite\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"connection\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"passions\", \"from\": 3205, \"to\": 3213}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3224}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3278, \"to\": 3287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And for me, like I was mentioning with my mental health, I need to fulfill those happy moments as a human too.\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mental health\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3370}, {\"ngram\": \"those happy moments\", \"from\": 3390, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"a human\", \"from\": 3413, \"to\": 3420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes it's so easy to be tunnel vision of your goals as an athlete.\", \"from\": 3426, \"to\": 3497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tunnel vision\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3468}, {\"ngram\": \"your goals\", \"from\": 3472, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 3486, \"to\": 3496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think when I do my best surfing is when I start painting more and writing poetry and connecting with people.\", \"from\": 3498, \"to\": 3608, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my best surfing\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"poetry\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3580}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And it's awesome to create those curated events in Southern California that I feel help me bring that community that I am looking for.\", \"from\": 3609, \"to\": 3743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those curated events\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3656}, {\"ngram\": \"Southern California\", \"from\": 3660, \"to\": 3679}, {\"ngram\": \"that community\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3720}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's an amazing partnership, and I love that they are really supporting women surfing.\", \"from\": 3744, \"to\": 3830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an amazing partnership\", \"from\": 3749, \"to\": 3771}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3821}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recently Hennessy wrote a poem that she shared on her social media about body positivity.\", \"from\": 3832, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hennessy\", \"from\": 3841, \"to\": 3849}, {\"ngram\": \"a poem\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3862}, {\"ngram\": \"her social media\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 3898}, {\"ngram\": \"body positivity\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is something she has found to focus on in her life and can now sh